    </div>

    <p><p>In order to maintain the quality level of dance training at Pacific Dance, classes run year-round.  Very often our classes are full, so space may be limited.   If you drop your class(es), your space in that class cannot be held.  If you have any questions, please feel free to speak with us.
    
